Sentencas: In this study, Ni/BaCe0.75Y0.25O3-delta (Ni/BCY25) was investigated as an anode for direct ammonia-fueled solid oxide fuel cells, The catalytic activity of Ni/BCY25 for ammonia decomposition was found to be remarkably higher than Ni/8 mol
Titulo: Electrochemical and Catalytic Properties of Ni/BaCe0.75Y0.25O3-δ Anode for Direct Ammonia-Fueled Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
